title: #92Noon! Birk/Krawczynski/Miller/Lavelle/Sinykin
description: PA is deeply troubled by The Christmas Day Calamity in New Orleans. Matt Birk joins for the Birk Bit. The Athletic's Jonny Krawczynski to discuss the Wolves. Voice of the Lions, Dan Miller ahead of Sunday's game. Lavelle E. Neal III has had enough of 2020, and the Sultan of Smug, Dave Sinykin.
